-- ESM to Pass High Court Test, Schaeuble Tells Bild am Sonntag
-- B y   E v a   v o n   S c h a p e r
-- 2012-09-09T14:49:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-09/esm-to-pass-high-court-test-schaeuble-tells-bild-am-sonntag.html
German Finance Minister  Wolfgang Schaeuble  sees  Germany ’s highest court dismissing a challenge to
the European Stability Mechanism, or ESM, when it rules on Sept.
12, Schaeuble said in an interview with Bild am  Sonntag .  The constitutionality of the ESM was “thoroughly” probed
at its inception, the newspaper cited Schaeuble as saying. The
Federal Constitutional Court has never seen the course of
European integration as being unconstitutional, Schaueble said
in the interview.  For Related News and Information:
